  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw Sword is a flying shooting game with minimalistic gameplay and roguelite elements.The single game is less than 20 minutes, the gameplay is simple, and the combat is very cool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/639874f890a29c707abdda491b8b9260.avif?t=1740648322\" width=748 height=896 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is full of Chinese fairy elements.Avoid enemy attacks and choose the right position to counter the enemy.Choose rewards to improve yourself.Hang in there and kill the final enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/f6c82f2dd8dde404f0b6f6ffce29c03b.poster.avif?t=1740648322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/f6c82f2dd8dde404f0b6f6ffce29c03b.webm?t=1740648322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/f6c82f2dd8dde404f0b6f6ffce29c03b.mp4?t=1740648322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 10 characters,15 basic skills,25 weapons, and many bonus items to choose from up to now. The choice of rewards is very important, and  the arrangement of skills and weapon also needs serious consideration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/700d9053319dbf63e2d158bd3d381bb8.poster.avif?t=1740648322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/700d9053319dbf63e2d158bd3d381bb8.webm?t=1740648322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/700d9053319dbf63e2d158bd3d381bb8.mp4?t=1740648322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw Sword is a flying shooting game with minimalistic gameplay and roguelite elements.The single game is less than 20 minutes, the gameplay is simple, and the combat is very cool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/639874f890a29c707abdda491b8b9260.avif?t=1740648322\" width=748 height=896 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is full of Chinese fairy elements.Avoid enemy attacks and choose the right position to counter the enemy.Choose rewards to improve yourself.Hang in there and kill the final enemy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/f6c82f2dd8dde404f0b6f6ffce29c03b.poster.avif?t=1740648322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/f6c82f2dd8dde404f0b6f6ffce29c03b.webm?t=1740648322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/f6c82f2dd8dde404f0b6f6ffce29c03b.mp4?t=1740648322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 10 characters,15 basic skills,25 weapons, and many bonus items to choose from up to now. The choice of rewards is very important, and  the arrangement of skills and weapon also needs serious consideration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/700d9053319dbf63e2d158bd3d381bb8.poster.avif?t=1740648322\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486680/extras/700d9053319dbf63e2d158b